{
  "ticket_id": "TASK-VIB-002",
  "title": "Enable All Governance Hooks",
  "description": "All hooks in `.github/hooks/policy-enforcement.json` and `.github/hooks/auto-sync.json` are set to `\"enabled\": false`. The hook scripts exist and are correct, but they are never fired. This means guardian STOP checks, `git add .` blocking, destructive operation blocking, and evidence verification are all silently bypassed at runtime.\n\nFix: Update both JSON files to set `\"enabled\": true` on every hook entry. Remove or update the `\"comment\"` fields noting the Preview status \u2014 the feature is now stable.",
